<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بَابُ الشِّجَاجِ وَكَسْرِ العِظَامِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">الشَّجَّةُ:</span> الجُرْحُ فِي الرَّأْسِ وَالوَجْهِ خَاصَّةً.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَهِيَ عَشْرٌ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">الحَارِصَةُ:</span> الَّتِي تَحْرِصُ الجِلْدَ -<span class="c5"> أَيْ:</span> تَشُقُّهُ قَلِيلاً، وَلَا تُدْمِيهِ -.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>ثُمَّ البَازِلَةُ - وَهِيَ الدَّامِيَةِ وَالدَّامِعَةُ - وَهِيَ الَّتِي يَسِيلُ مِنْهَا الدَّمُ -.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>ثُمَّ البَاضِعَةُ؛<span class="c5"> وَهِيَ:</span> الَّتِي تَبْضَعُ اللَّحْمَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>ثُمَّ المُتَلَاحِمَةُ؛<span class="c5"> وَهِيَ:</span> الغَائِصَةُ فِي اللَّحْمِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>ثُمَّ السِّمْحَاقُ؛<span class="c5"> وَهِيَ:</span> مَا بَيْنَهَا وَبَيْنَ العَظْمِ قِشْرَةٌ رَقِيقَةٌ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">فَهَذِهِ الخَمْسُ:</span> لَا مُقَدَّرَ فِيهَا؛ بَلْ حُكُومَةٌ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">وَفِي المُوضِحَةِ وَهِيَ:</span> مَا تُوضِحُ العَظْمَ وَتُبْرِزُهُ: خَمْسَةُ أَبْعِرَةٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>